org.jscsi.target.scsi.modeSense

Enum ModePageCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ModePageCode>
      • org.jscsi.target.scsi.modeSense.ModePageCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ModePageCode>

    public enum ModePageCode
extends Enum<ModePageCode>
    Mode Pages for direct-access block devices, as defined in SBC-3.

    Instances of this enumeration are used to identify a requested or a returned ModePage.

    Author:
    Andreas Ergenzinger
